-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Debian Packaging

To create a Debian package, run the following commands from the top level
directory (ie. the one with the following files/dirs):

 $ cd /path/to/pgpatcher
 $ ls -F
 bin/  db/  debian/  Makefile  README
 $ fakeroot dpkg-buildpackage
 ...etc...
 $ ls ../*.deb
 ../pgpatcher_0.1.0_all.deb
 $ lintian ../*.deb
 $

